Package com.github.dscpsyl.jgrade2.gradedtest

Annotation Interface GradedTest

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(METHOD) public @interface GradedTest
The GradedTest annotation is primarily based off of capturing the data for a test object in the Gradescope JSON output. They are used to create corresponding GradedTestResult objects. Uses a String for the name of the test (default "Unnamed test") , a String for the question number (default ""), a double for the number of points the test is worth(defaults to 1.0), and a String for the visibility of the test (defaults to "visible").
